rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Workbook
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A spreadsheet document, for example from Excel. Each spreadsheet contains a set of sheets that hold actual data.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Documentation
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Links some entity to a document, which might provide further detail or evidence regarding the entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Country of destination
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Final destination for the goods

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: D-U-N-S
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Dun & Bradstreet identifier

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Declarant
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Customs declarant

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Website
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Website address

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Parent company
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: If this entity is a subsidiary, another entity (company or organisation) is its parent

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Description
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Description of goods

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Federal tax service code
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (RU, ФНС) Federal Tax Service related info

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: COD CAEM
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (RO) What kind of activity a legal entity is allowed to develop

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: USD Exchange Rate
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: USD Exchange Rate for the activity

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Family
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Family relationship between two people

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Date
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: If not otherwise specified

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Sampling Rate
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Sampling rate of the audio in Hz

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: City
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: City, town, village or other locality

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Bank Account
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Bank account of the contract

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Person
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The subject of the association.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Remarks
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Handling instructions, like 'care of'.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Bank account
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An account held at a bank and controlled by an owner. This may also be used to describe more complex arrangements like correspondent bank settlement accounts.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Contract
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An contract or contract lot issued by an authority. Multiple lots may be awarded to different suppliers (see ContractAward).

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Foreign currency bank
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Bank account for payments in foreign currency

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: FSS
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (RU, ФСС) Social Security

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Public body
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A public body, such as a ministry, department or state company.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Legal entity
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Any party to legal proceedings, such as asset ownership, corporate governance or social interactions. Often used when raw data does not specify if something is a person or company.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Rouble bank
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Bank account for payments in roubles

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: State
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: State or federal unit.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: ICIJ ID
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: ID according to International Consortium for Investigative Journalists

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: The language of the translated text
E-Mail
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Email address

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: INN
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Russian company ID

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Security
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A tradeable financial asset.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Contract holder
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Customs formalities caretaker

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Registration number
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Company registration number

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Phone
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Phone number

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Cryptocurrency wallet
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A cryptocurrency wallet is a view on the transactions conducted by one participant on a blockchain / distributed ledger system.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Customs Value Amount
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Customs Value of goods

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Company
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A corporation, usually for profit. Does not distinguish between private and public companies, and can also be used to model more specific constructs like trusts and funds. Companies are assets, so they can be owned by other legal entities.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Contract award
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A contract or contract lot as awarded to a supplier.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: BCC
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Blind carbon copy

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: PO Box
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A mailbox indentifier at the post office

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: License
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A grant of land, rights or property. A type of Contract

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Sender
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Origin of the goods

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Tax Number
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Tax identification number

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Translated version of the body text
SWIFT/BIC
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Bank identifier code

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: IRS Number
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: US tax ID

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Identification
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An form of identification associated with its holder and some issuing country. This can be used for national ID cards, voter enrollments and similar instruments.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Relationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Nature of the relationship, from the person's perspective eg. 'mother', where 'relative' is mother of 'person'.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Supplier
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The entity the contract was awarded to

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Asset
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A piece of property which can be owned and assigned a monetary value.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Airplane
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An airplane, helicopter or other flying vehicle.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Project
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An activity carried out by a group of participants.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Debt
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A monetary debt between two parties.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Relative
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The relative of the subject person.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Tax roll
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A tax declaration of an individual

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Person
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A natural person, as opposed to a corporation of some type.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Post
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A post, role or position held by an individual within an organization or body. This describes the period for which the position is held, not the abstract concept of the post.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Vessel
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A boat or ship. Typically flying some sort of national flag.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Representation
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A mediatory, intermediary, middleman, or broker acting on behalf of a legal entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: FEAC Code
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (Код ТН ВЭД) Foreign Economic Activity Commodity Code

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Package
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A bundle of files that have been packaged together into some form of archive.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Real estate
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A piece of land or property.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Relationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Nature of the association

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Dissolution date
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The date the legal entity was dissolved, if applicable

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: The language of the translated text
Person
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The subject of the familial relation.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Country of origin
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Country of origin of goods

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Duration
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Duration of the video in ms

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Payment programme
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Programme name, funding code, category identifier, etc.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VOEN
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Azerbaijan taxpayer ID

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Associate
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An associate of the subject person.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: In Reply To
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Message ID of the preceding email in the thread

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Document
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A multi-page document, such as a PDF or Word file or slide-show presentation.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: OKVED(2) Classifier
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (RU, ОКВЭД) Economical activity classifier. OKVED2 is the same but newer

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: OKPO
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Russian industry classifier

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Image
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An image file.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: CPV code
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Contract Procurement Vocabulary (what type of goods/services, EU)

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Interval
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An object which is bounded in time.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Trading Country
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Trading Country of the company which transports the goods via Russian border

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: In Reply To
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Message ID of the preceding message in the thread

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Amended
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Was this award amended, modified or updated by a subsequent document?

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Country of origin
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Primary country of this entity

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: SEC Central Index Key
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: US SEC Central Index Key

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Encumbrance
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An encumbrance is a right to, interest in, or legal liability on real property that does not prohibit passing title to the property but that diminishes its value.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Jurisdiction
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Country or region in which this entity operates

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Payment
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A monetary payment between two parties.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Duration
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Duration of the audio in ms

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: ID Number
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: ID number of any applicable ID

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Postal code
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Zip code or postcode.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Transport
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Means of transportation

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Author
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The original author, not the uploader

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Type
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Type of contract. Potentially W (Works), U (Supplies), S (Services).

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: NUTS code
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Nomencalture of Territorial Units for Statistics (NUTS)

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Organization
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Any type of incorporated entity that cannot be owned by another (see Company). This might include charities, foundations or state-owned enterprises, depending on their juristiction.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: OKSM
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Russian (ОКСМ) countries classifer

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Crawler
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The crawler used to acquire this file

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Checksum
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: SHA1 hash of the data

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Project participant
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An activity carried out by a group of participants.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Country of departure
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Country out of which the goods are transported

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: LEI
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Legal Entity Identifier

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Incorporation date
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The date the legal entity was incorporated

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: OKOPF
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (RU, ОКОПФ) What kind of business entity

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: KPP
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (RU, КПП) in addition to INN for orgs; reason for registration at FNS

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: V.A.T. Identifier
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (EU) VAT number

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Succession
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Two entities that legally succeed each other.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Note
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An annotation that applies to a document or entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: BIK
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Russian bank account code

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: OGRN
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Major State Registration Number

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: ISIN
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: International Securities Identification Number

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Region
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Also province or area.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Generator
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The program used to generate this file

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Analyzable
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An entity suitable for being processed via named-entity recognition.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Invoice Value Amount
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Invoice Value of goods

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Address
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Public key used to identify the wallet

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Translated version of the body text
Address
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A location associated with an entity.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Direction of transportation
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Direction of transportation (import/export)

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Message ID
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Message ID of a document; unique in most cases

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Article
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A piece of media reporting about a subject.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Sanction
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A sanction designation

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Similar
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A link between two entities that are presumed to be the same, e.g. as the outcome of a probabilistic record linkage process.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: E-Mail
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An internet mail message. The body can be formatted as plain text and/or HTML, and the message may have any number of attachments.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: CCD Value
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Declaration Value

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Receiver
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Destination of the goods

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: FEAC Code description
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (Описание кода ТН ВЭД) Foreign Economic Activity Commodity Code description

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Customs declaration
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A foreign economic activity

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Text file
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Text files, like .txt or source code.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Table
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A document structured into rows and cells. This includes simple CSV files, spreadsheet sheets or database relations.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Customs Procedure
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Customs Procedure — type of customs clearance

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: PFR Number
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: (RU, ПФР) Pension Fund Registration number. AAA-BBB-CCCCCC, where AAA is organisation region, BBB is district, CCCCCC number at a specific branch

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: CC
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Carbon copy

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Associate
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Non-family association between two people

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: JIB
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Yugoslavia company ID

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Passport
rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An passport held by a person.
